# Environment Rules

Never access:

```ts
import.meta.env
```

directly outside:

```txt
config/env.ts
```

Always create:

```ts
const Environment = {
  API_BASE_URL:
    import.meta.env.VITE_API_BASE_URL
};

export default Environment;
```

Rules:

- All environment variables must be mapped through env.ts
- Never hardcode URLs
- Never expose secrets
- Validate required variables

